{"tid":783412,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"法國啲香港人原來好鐘意睇人跳樓","createTime":"2018-08-17T13:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T14:47:20.000Z","uid":191338,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2008a83078c89f056b85eb481d5b2e98ef725461","tid":783412,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T13:42:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">個種熱衷程度比睇波仲要狂熱</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/213119_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F213119_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7706a04d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我在樓上看風景<br />\n觀景樓下人看我<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/17/213812_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F17%2F213812_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ab28c003&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母係跳就快撚啲跳咪撚阻住呀叔收工啦<br />\n街坊如是說<br />\n<br />\n仆你個臭街阻鳩住地球轉搞撚到巴士塞成粒鐘都未郁過<br />\n打工仔如是說"},{"pid":"7ec0ef84c82fbb90742f4266d4ad93b1d7ae3ed7","tid":783412,"uid":190604,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T13:46:50.000Z","msg":"之前試過路過有人想跳樓<br />\n又係一班人企係下面影<br />\n影影影<br />\n係咪咩都要影一餐？<br />\n好似睇戲咁睇<br />\n仲要講埋啲好難聽嘅說話<br />\n有冇人性㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9d649fdd365465a37cacce922900eed93ef029","tid":783412,"uid":191338,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T13:53:08.000Z","msg":"我覺得以後跳樓唔應該派消防放氣墊<br />\n<br />\n應該搵隊人走去拉橫額<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">跳樓仆街落地獄不得好死</span><br />\n<br />\n或者搵定隊喃嘸佬係樓下standby<br />\n吹奏啲打準備即時超渡<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">西方極樂一路好走</span><br />\n<br />\n如果係耶教仲簡單<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">到我這裡來，我給你永生</span>"},{"pid":"fc8098763b132c7e051b0de49f7abca8386c56ec","tid":783412,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:08:28.000Z","msg":"一嘢跳落嚟擲鳩死班仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"769f2670ee7e1000abb1f1642cebbedc123656db","tid":783412,"uid":152047,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:09:22.000Z","msg":"其實有咩好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔係記者又棟響條路度影影影，塞撚條路又影響救援"},{"pid":"04070536c82eb5ef647241bc4b1eab5c02c4295c","tid":783412,"uid":191338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:15:20.000Z","msg":"好似當年08奧運會咁充滿激情<br />\n<br />\n如果隔離單位又爬個人出黎企跳應該會更精彩<br />\n<br />\n有競爭先有進步嘛"},{"pid":"b8d534fcf9faef2a3811b1236d9dec77bd114d6b","tid":783412,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:28:58.000Z","msg":"原本就真係你死你賤關人撚事嘅<br />\n不過因為你嘅死而影響到人，人地想你死都好正常呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5d6b000e076d842d064716d75aed2a8de187a5","tid":783412,"uid":173853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:35:34.000Z","msg":"我唔撚信條友跌落變肉醬 班撚樣仲圍住喺度影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個社會病態到咁"},{"pid":"7470db9673ae13291d7263a72e0cad73df5c2f6f","tid":783412,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f5d6b000e076d842d064716d75aed2a8de187a5","tid":783412,"uid":173853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:35:34.000Z","msg":"我唔撚信條友跌落變肉醬 班撚樣仲圍住喺度影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個社會病態到咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T14:38:54.000Z","msg":"香港人冇咩娛樂<br />\n<br />\n學古羅馬起個競技場<br />\n比啲想跳樓嘅去參加<br />\n門票180/380/680/1380"},{"pid":"325981b3d77d53132d014421c1043f1430131420","tid":783412,"uid":79077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0